604170001"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.personal-knowledge-management","id":"zettel.moc.personal-knowledge-management","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":3,"offset":594},"end":{"line":13,"column":26,"offset":617},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.202604170001"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.personal-knowledge-management","id":"zettel.moc.personal-knowledge-management","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":767},"end":{"line":21,"column":26,"offset":790},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.202604170001"}],"anchors":{"gagasan":{"type":"header","text":"Gagasan","value":"gagasan","line":16,"column":0,"depth":2},"mengapa-ini-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Mengapa Ini Penting","value":"mengapa-ini-penting","line":24,"column":0,"depth":2},"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain":{"type":"header","text":"Hubungan ke Zettel Lain","value":"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain","line":33,"column":0,"depth":2},"sumber":{"type":"header","text":"Sumber","value":"sumber","line":38,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"second-brain-memperluas-kapasitas-berpikir-dengan-memindahkan-beban-memori-ke-sistem-eksternal\">Second brain memperluas kapasitas berpikir dengan memindahkan beban memori ke sistem eksternal<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#second-brain-memperluas-kapasitas-berpikir-dengan-memindahkan-beban-memori-ke-sistem-eksternal\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"gagasan\">Gagasan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#gagasan\"></a></h2>\n<p>Otak manusia sangat terbatas sebagai tempat penyimpanan — <em>working memory</em> hanya bisa menampung 4±1 item sekaligus (Miller's Law direvisi Cowan). Tapi otak sangat handal dalam membuat <em>koneksi</em> dan menghasilkan <em>insight</em>.</p>\n<p>\"Second brain\" — sistem catatan eksternal yang terstruktur — membebaskan kapasitas kognitif dari beban menyimpan, dan mengalihkannya ke tugas yang lebih tinggi: <strong>berpikir, menghubungkan, dan menciptakan</strong>.</p>\n<p>Ini bukan soal malas mengingat. Ini soal <em>optimalkan otak untuk tugasnya yaitu berpikir</em>, bukan <em>mengingat</em>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"mengapa-ini-penting\">Mengapa Ini Penting<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#mengapa-ini-penting\"></a></h2>\n<p>Kalau kamu mencoba menyimpan semua ide di kepala, kamu akan selalu kehabisan \"RAM\". Akibatnya kamu:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Takut lupa → anxious</li>\n<li>Tidak berani move on dari satu topik ke topik lain</li>\n<li>Kehilangan ide bagus yang datang di waktu yang tidak tepat</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Dengan sistem eksternal yang dipercaya, otak bisa <em>melepas</em> dan fokus pada tugas saat ini.</p>\n<h2 id=\"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\">Hubungan ke Zettel Lain<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Mendukung <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170002\">Ide yang tidak ditulis sama dengan ide yang tidak ada</a> — karena kalau ada sistem eksternal yang dipercaya, kamu <em>harus</em> menuliskan ide setiap kali muncul agar sistem bekerja</li>\n<li>Mendasari <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170003\">Koneksi antar gagasan lebih bernilai dari koleksi informasi</a> — karena nilai sistem eksternal bukan di jumlah catatannya, tapi di koneksi yang terbentuk antar gagasan di dalamnya</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sumber\">Sumber<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sumber\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain\">Literature Note — Building a Second Brain</a> — Bab 2: \"What Is a Second Brain?\"</li>\n<li>David Allen, <em>Getting Things Done</em> — \"Your mind is for having ideas, not holding them\"</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #a03623;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.zettel\">zettel</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #f0944d;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.knowledge-management\">knowledge-management</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #952e8f;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.cognitive-science\">cognitive-science</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/notes.zettelkasten\">Zettelkasten di Dendron — Panduan Implementasi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170002\">Ide yang tidak ditulis sama dengan ide yang tidak ada</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170003\">Koneksi antar gagasan lebih bernilai dari koleksi informasi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/notes.zettelkasten.cara-pakai\">Cara Pakai Zettelkasten di Project Ini</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain\">Literature Note — Building a Second Brain</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.personal-knowledge-management\">MOC: Personal Knowledge Management</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":